::Prowl/Striker::

Prowl's eyes widen as he hears the bot declare itself Dinobot. He frowns, but 
puts on a neutral expression as he catches Iron Raptor's look.

Standing near Cyber Claw, Striker, however, does not catch Iron Raptor's 
look. The maximal looks at the new bot, a frown on his face.

"Wait," he says to Cyber Claw, contradicting Iron Raptor's invitation, 
"Didn't you run off with Tavatron?"
